issue.body:
This issue comes from #55739
`src` and `tgt` should be the same.
```c
int src (int c)
{
  return ((2 << c) & 15) != 0;
}

int tgt (int c)
{
  return (unsigned)c <= 2;
}

```
https://godbolt.org/z/fPYEYrjbG
https://alive2.llvm.org/ce/z/pS2xu2

